	Title: Halloween Playtest now available!
	Author: Oliver Brakmann
	Content: Today we have started the countdown to our next stable release with a new OpenRA Halloween playtest!\n\nGlobal lobby chat, game speed settings, balance changes, new missions, improved performance: we have all sorts of tricks and treats in store for you today!\n\nHead over to our website at http://openra.net to read all about the good things coming your way, or read the detailed changelog at http://changelog.openra.net.\n\nWe rely on your feedback to make the next release as awesome as possible, so please give this playtest a try and report any and all problems you encounter at http://bugs.openra.net. Thanks, and have fun!